cleaned_text: What we're about This meetup is for North Jersey communities to meet, learn and share about health, wellness and natural living lifestyle. We will host various events and speakers about a variety of topics regarding Health and Wellness. Some topics may be: The Functional Medicine, Integrative Medicine, Homeopathic Medicine, Natural Healing techniques, Nutrition, Kids Health, Feng shui, Meditation, Acupuncture, Skin care, Reiki, Hypnosis, Stress management, Tai Chi, Natural Homes, Sustainable Environment etc. Please let us know what topics are of interest to you and we will custom tailor our programs to your needs. Looking forward to meeting you soon! Natural Awakenings of Northern
